  "texts": [
    "In this regard, future work may examine the implications of memory updates on model outputs.",
    "7.2.4 Supporting post-interaction reflection.",
    "Although existing work on human-chatbot interaction for mental well-being has predominantly focused on engaging users during conversations [48,49], our study demonstrates that post-interaction reflection is also a promising avenue for enhancing individuals' awareness and developing skills for better prompt creation.",
    "Participants often revisited past conversations and expressed curiosity about how their interactions with the chatbot might affect their overall mental well-being.",
    "Therefore, they proposed ideas around memory presentations, such as summarizing frequently discussed topics, tracking the time spent talking to the chatbot, and exploring possible connections between their interactions and their mood changes."
  ],
